\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.080394516992446e-12, \"text\": \"NFL MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\"}, {\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"score\": 0.9999999999968168, \"rank\": 3.080394516992446e-12, \"text\": \"NFL MVP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League_Most_Valuable_Player_Award\"}, {\"begin\": 330, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999987931726543, \"rank\": 7.083719893456686e-07, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mike Tirico\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tirico\"}, {\"begin\": 396, \"end\": 410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manning said he would not have considered this opportunity if it were not for Tirico.\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  \\\"I kind of argued with him as to why he and NBC thought I was worthy,\\\" Manning toldThe Athletic's Andrew Marchand.\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 559, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sunday_Night_Football\", \"score\": 0.8577077803282064, \"rank\": 0.16584891303356808, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sunday_Night_Football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sunday_Night_Football\"}, {\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marchand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Marchand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He said they were bringing in Kelly Clarkson to kind of give the perspective of a fan and wanted me to share the perspective of what these athletes are thinking about it.\\\"\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 661, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Manning, 47, played in the NFL from 1998 to 2015 with theIndianapolis Colts(1998 to 2011) andDenver Broncos(2012 to 2015).\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9734999321441372, \"rank\": 0.021310921962940623, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to his Super Bowls and MVPs, Manning was a 14-time Pro Bowler, a seven-time first-team All-Pro, a four-time NFL touchdowns leader and a three-time NFL passing yards leader.\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9734999321441372, \"rank\": 0.021310921962940623, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \".\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"@kellyclarkson, Peyton Manning and@miketiricowill be hosting the@NBCOlympicsopening ceremony!#FallonTonightpic.twitter.com/bz5FJMdHeq  - The Tonight Show (@FallonTonight)March 13, 2024    In his post-football career, Manning founded Omaha Productions, a media and entertainment company known for producing the alternative live broadcast of ESPN's \\\"Monday Night Football\\\" called the \\\"ManningCast,\\\" hosted by Peyton and Eli Manning.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1130, \"end\": 1144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Peyton Manning\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\"}, {\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omaha_Nighthawks\", \"score\": 0.999985814653087, \"rank\": 1.4118553232915999e-05, \"text\": \"Omaha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omaha_Nighthawks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omaha_Nighthawks\"}, {\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.371096536587602e-19, \"text\": \"ESPN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ESPN\"}, {\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"score\": 0.9999999655728976, \"rank\": 3.442729875455046e-08, \"text\": \"ManningCast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\"}, {\"begin\": 1521, \"end\": 1527, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4984655323479808e-36, \"text\": \"Peyton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\"}, {\"begin\": 1532, \"end\": 1543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eli_Manning\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eli Manning\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eli_Manning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eli_Manning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"ManningCast\\\" debuted in September 2021.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1550, \"end\": 1561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"score\": 0.9999999655728976, \"rank\": 3.442729875455046e-08, \"text\": \"ManningCast\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peyton_Manning\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 opening ceremony will be the first to not occur in a stadium.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2603767199815441e-14, \"text\": \